node.text:
What if Doraemon delivers Matcha Azuki pancake dorayaki for you for breakfast?
🤗
I got this 4 kinds set of Pancake Dorayaki Pandora valued box from @pancakecafe_belleville.
😊
They come with 4 flavours:
Classic
Matcha Azuki
Cream and Custard
Premium Cream and Custard with Strawberry
😄
No Min order. Delivery islandwide for small fee. WhatsApp 92968162 to place the order.
